I love this place! We bought two sofas from another place, came here for some outdoor furniture and found our sofas.. Exact same stuff,  for over $1,000 less. We used to go to American a lot when we lived in Denver,  and we're beyond thrilled they came to the Valley. This is the only place we get furniture.. Period! It's quality brands,  but WAAAYYYYY less than other stores. We live in North Scottsdale, and will make the drive here instead of going to the overpriced places up North. Amazing furniture plus killer prices... Yep, this is the place to go!

